descriptionNullable:
The dataset consists of labelled credit card transactions happened across a pool of 600 merchants as fraud or not fraud gathered over a period of 2-3 years.
It is a good resource for learning, practicing or testing beginner to intermediate ML tasks like Classification, Prediction, Anomaly Detection and Time Series Analysis.
Working with this dataset and trying to achieve good score at results will give you hands-on  exposure to class imbalance problems.
